01:24.718 --> 01:29.323 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: One after another,
they made the
pilgrimage to Trump Tower for
audiences with

01:29.356 --> 01:31.224 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the president-elect.

01:31.258 --> 01:36.530 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
