we're right
on target, right on time for all
of that.

02:09.162 --> 02:13.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: President-elect Trump
talked foreign
policy with former Secretary of
State Henry

02:13.300 --> 02:15.068 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Kissinger.

02:15.102 --> 02:19.439 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
