President-Elect: Very
humbling to be back among my
former colleagues

02:56.843 --> 03:01.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
who are excited about moving the
Trump agenda
forward in the coming Congress,
and I'm just

03:01.648 --> 03:03.950 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
so grateful, so grateful for the
warm hospitality.

03:03.984 --> 03:09.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
