down with House
Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi,
and with Chuck

03:09.623 --> 03:12.559 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Schumer, the incoming Senate
minority leader.

03:12.592 --> 03:14.895 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm John
Yang.

03:14.928 --> 03:18.398 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Former House
Speaker Newt
Gingrich took himself out of the
running for

03:18.432 --> 03:20.400 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
