wants the freedom
to -- quote -- "network across
the whole system."

03:24.471 --> 03:28.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In the day's
other news: President
Obama had some pointed advice
for his successor

03:28.975 --> 03:30.744 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on dealing with Russia.

03:30.777 --> 03:35.582 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
