when it goes
too far.

03:38.618 --> 03:45.659 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
My hope is, is that he does not
simply take

03:45.692 --> 03:53.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
