themselves whether
America is the country we
thought it was.

04:29.302 --> 04:35.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But please listen to me when I
say this: America
is worth it.

04:35.041 --> 04:37.344 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Our children are worth it.

04:37.377 --> 04:42.315 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
