for our values,
and never, ever give up.

04:42.349 --> 04:45.352 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Clinton didn't
mention president-elect
Trump by name.

04:45.385 --> 04:49.156 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
