today that
he will run against Pelosi.

05:08.441 --> 05:13.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The U.S.
surgeon general
is out with a call to action on
substance

05:13.446 --> 05:14.514 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
abuse.

05:14.548 --> 05:16.650 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
