overdoses of
all kinds in 2014.

05:26.693 --> 05:32.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And more than 27 million people
reported using
illegal drugs or misusing
prescription drugs

05:32.399 --> 05:34.134 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
