for another
interest rate hike next month.

05:43.610 --> 05:46.846 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Janet Yellen gave her
semi-annual report to
Congress today.

05:46.880 --> 05:51.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She acknowledged the Fed's view
could change,
depending on what the Trump
administration

05:51.384 --> 05:53.153 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
