and inflation
and perhaps adjust our outlook
depending on

06:14.074 --> 06:15.775 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
what happens.

06:15.809 --> 06:20.413 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Yellen also said
she has no
intention of stepping down
before her term

