10.

06:51.678 --> 06:55.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Astronaut
Peggy Whitson
is now the oldest woman in space
at the age

06:55.649 --> 06:57.417 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
