price-fixing
scandal.

07:30.950 --> 07:34.921 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ADM was also a major underwriter
of the "NewsHour"
for years.

07:34.954 --> 07:37.324 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
