07:56.076 --> 08:06.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: President-elect
Trump has spoken
by phone to scores of world
leaders.

08:06.353 --> 08:11.491 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
