09:02.842 --> 09:03.843 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHAEL PILLSBURY, Former U.S.
Assistant Undersecretary
of Defense: It's common.

09:03.877 --> 09:05.945 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
