sets up a competitive
dynamic.

09:24.864 --> 09:29.035 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's been some approaches
already now already
from Prime Minister Modi of
India and other

09:29.068 --> 09:32.672 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
