to have a chance
to talk to the president-elect
as well.

09:32.705 --> 09:35.108 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But you're saying
it's common,
this is something that is
normally done?

09:35.141 --> 09:36.910 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL PILLSBURY: I don't the
statistics.

09:36.943 --> 09:39.712 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
The key thing is, the
president-elect can't
act.

09:39.746 --> 09:43.750 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
