stupidity of our
own consciousness in life.

51:20.544 --> 51:24.615 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We are ribbing ourselves, our
own pretensions,
our own middle class.

51:24.648 --> 51:28.552 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And in doing that, of course, we
become connoisseurs
of unhappiness.

51:28.585 --> 51:32.890 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Cartoonists' relationship to
rejection depends
on the cartoonist.

51:32.923 --> 51:35.893 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
An amateur loves everything they
do and think
everything is perfect.

51:35.926 --> 51:40.397 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
A professional really
understands that, in
the end, somebody else has to
judge their

51:40.431 --> 51:42.232 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
work.

51:42.266 --> 51:45.536 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Often something that comes out
of your own
real-life experience, you don't
directly use.

51:45.569 --> 51:47.338 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You modify it within the form.

51:47.371 --> 51:49.606 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I was on the phone and someone
was brushing
me off.

51:49.640 --> 51:51.775 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So I just said to them, how
about never?

51:51.809 --> 51:52.977 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Is never good for you?

51:53.010 --> 51:55.512 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Then I tweaked it to make it
into a cartoon.

51:55.546 --> 51:59.483 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
That has the syntax of
politeness, and yet
the message is rude.

51:59.516 --> 52:04.989 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that duality is really the
essence of
humor, that type of surprise.

52:05.022 --> 52:09.526 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
